ootball/2023/aug/09/lina-hurtig-var-penalty-tattoo-if-sweden-win-fifa-world-cup-2023" target="_blank">Lina Hurtig considers VAR penalty tattoo if Sweden win World Cup</a></h2><div class="description"> Arsenal winger Lina Hurtig came off the bench in the 81st minute of the last-16 clash. Arsenal winger struck the seventh penalty in a wild shootout that saw Sweden beat USA 5-4. VAR image showed how close ball was to going over line to go over line.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Wed, 09 Aug 2023 01:16:58 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">sports</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/09/lina-hurtig-var-penalty-tattoo-if-sweden-win-fifa-world-cup-2023" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2023/aug/09/the-spin-ben-stokes-england-test-selection-india-tour-cricket" target="_blank">The Spin | Test selection is set to get interesting, whether Ben Stokes likes it or not</a></h2><div class="description"> England captain Ben Stokes yearns to make selection boring. Selection has become a game that even the selectors themselves can barely be bothered to play. The England captain spoiled the fun of armchair selectors with consistent sides during Ashes but must make adjustments for India tour.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Wed, 09 Aug 2023 10:29:29 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2023/aug/09/the-spin-ben-stokes-england-test-selection-india-tour-cricket" target="_blank">Click h