 class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/football/2023/aug/09/wolves-julen-lopetegui-how-it-went-wrong" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2023/aug/09/wembley-womens-challenge-cup-final-rugby-league-lois-forsell-leeds-st-helens" target="_blank">Wembley Challenge Cup final another giant step for women’s rugby league</a></h2><div class="description"> Women’s Challenge Cup final will take place at Wembley for the first time. Leeds Rhinos take on holders St Helens in a rematch of last year's decider. Leeds coach Lois Forsell: 'It's huge for future generations,’ says Forsell.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Wed, 09 Aug 2023 13:23:35 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">sports</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2023/aug/09/wembley-womens-challenge-cup-final-rugby-league-lois-forsell-leeds-st-helens" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2023/aug/09/warren-gatland-changes-entire-wales-lineup-england-clash-rugby-world-cup-warmup" target="_blank">Warren Gatland changes entire Wales lineup for England clash</a></h2><div class="description"> Wales face England at Twickenham on Saturday afternoon. Joe Roberts makes his Wales debut, with Dewi Lake as captain. Owen Williams starts at fly-half, Tom Rogers on wing and Taine Plumtree at No 8. Zander Fagerson sent off after being sent off for Wales' 20-9 win over England.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Wed, 09 Aug 2023 13:00:23 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">sports</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: